{"tid":799282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉殺妻藏屍今提堂 控方透露張祺忠聲稱有自殺傾向","createTime":"2018-08-30T02:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T03:38:08.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"692349e42a846d9c019fd0a325a78f087b9e7491","tid":799282,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T02:58:40.000Z","msg":"涉殺妻藏屍今提堂 控方透露張祺忠聲稱有自殺傾向<br />\n<br />\n港大校委會成員、機械工程學系副教授張祺忠涉兩周前在宿舍殺妻後伴屍多天，繼而將屍體運往其於黃克競樓的辦公室隱藏。警方日前突擊搜查張辦公室發現藏屍木箱，昨控告他一項謀殺罪，今在東區法院提堂。被告暫毋須答辯，案件押後至11月22日待警方進一步調查。控方申請被告還押懲教期間需特別看管，透露被告聲稱有自殺傾向。<br />\n<br />\n穿拖鞋到庭應訊的張祺忠（53歲）今上庭時一臉平靜。控罪指他於本月17日，在香港西區沙宣道6號香港大學偉倫堂內謀殺女子陳慧文。書記向他讀出控罪，張表示明白。辯方不反對押後，亦沒有任何申請。<br />\n<br />\n張祺忠好友浸大生物系前研究助理教授王凱峰、港大教職員會主席張星煒等，今亦到庭旁聽。<br />\n【案件編號：ESCC2107/18】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180830/58623588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180830%2F58623588&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ba52e3f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180830%2F58623588&h=c51075d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180830/58623588</a>"},{"pid":"9193eb6cf71f3f8409d4b3790e63f38acf727611","tid":799282,"uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"已經黐撚咗線"},{"pid":"0e31b2dad78a8072f67a82d922a8c3263191ee56","tid":799282,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"想自殺 close file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89b833fc9b636524ee17fcad1ef6158897ed47c","tid":799282,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9193eb6cf71f3f8409d4b3790e63f38acf727611","tid":799282,"uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"已經黐撚咗線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:23:12.000Z","msg":"咁睇來我地諗多左，教授應該有精神病"},{"pid":"59bc9a67ab63c8f3e7f8d67a8888f9ce7aab0a23","tid":799282,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9163ac45655294727e372771eba2fff7b22b9fb","tid":799282,"uid":47641,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"自殺滅囗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbefdb9eaa4300ff51d3b4a276a91dfb90e15a9b","tid":799282,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:35:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f14898d4a4921697de3a5a81ccb65950fcf6c703","tid":799282,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"死左就攬哂罪名<br />\n無人知真相"}]}